                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9044" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">MKT-1372</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2856 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">童书妈妈：如何经营阅读写作社群？</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Tongshumama: how to run a reading and writing community？</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">周文辉，陈家兴</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中南大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">北京三川滔滔文化传播有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">服务业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中小型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">17 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">3C模型；品牌社群4C法则；麦肯锡信任公式；AARRR模型；上瘾模型；2024百优案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">3C&#39;s Strategic Triangle Model; brand community 4Cs; Mckinsey Trust Equation; AARRR model; hook model</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">随着素质教育迎来政策红利期，市场竞争愈发激烈，正当各家教育企业苦恼于如何降低获客成本和提高客单价时，童书妈妈另辟蹊径，以追问教育本质为使命驱动，十年探索，逆流而上，通过阅读写作社群获得了40多个国家、百万用户的喜爱，并且将许多忠诚用户转化成为创业伙伴。品牌社群如何定位？如何进行品牌内容创作与传播？如何建立用户信任？如何实现用户价值持续增长？本案例以问题为导向，通过时间线和事件线描述了童书妈妈经营阅读写作社群的背景、过程、决策情境与决策问题。本案例将思政元素有机地融入到案例分析中，引导学员思考新时代背景下融贯“小我”与“大我”，厚植家国情怀，追求义利共赢，寓价值观引导于理论知识传授和能力培养中，凸显德育因素。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">As well-rounded education comes to a policy dividend period and market competition becomes more and more fierce, while various education companies are distressed about acquisition and profit, Tongshumama regards pursuing the essence of education as its mission. Ten years of exploration, through the reading and writing community, Tongshumama has won the love of more than 40 countries and millions of users. Meanwhile, it turns many loyal users into entrepreneurial partners. How to position the brand community? How to create and disseminate the content? How to build user trust? How to achieve sustained growth in user value? This case is problem-oriented and describes the background, process, decision-making context and problems of Tongshumama reading and writing community through time line and event line. At the same time, this paper organically integrates ideological and political elements into the case analysis, guiding students to deeply understand of the integration of individual and nation, cultivate a strong sense of patriotic sentiment, pursuing the unity of social and economic values, aiming at knowledge imparting and ability development with value driving and highlighting moral education factors.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《营销管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">品牌社群的价值意义；品牌社群定位3C模型；引爆社群4C法则；麦肯锡信任公式；品牌社群用户价值增长AARRR模型；上瘾模型</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-12</td>
                            </tr>
